Tame, but pretty cool.<EOS> I can’t wait to show Toph and Len.<EOS> 

Cara has chocolate smeared on her mouth, but she lets me wipe her face off.<EOS> 

“You ready to go back to see Mom?” I say.<EOS> 

When we pass Spencer’s again, she stops.<EOS> “Uhhh,” she says, pointing to the
